Technical Details:
This entire project relies of Whisper STT and Coqui TTS integrated with Silero VAD which is responsible for the smooth flow of the AI system. 
This system is built with the in house used AI integrated into this project on a service layer level such that the API KEY is not exposed on the front end, hence maintaining security protocals.
